## Limitations
The findings are based on available literature and may not cover all possible factors influencing disaster risks. The search was limited to English-language sources and may not include insights from non-English publications. Additionally, the dynamic nature of disasters means that new factors may emerge over time, necessitating ongoing research and adaptation of disaster preparedness strategies.